1
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:05,080
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:10,190
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:15,330
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,330 --> 00:00:22,750
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:30,710
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,710 --> 00:00:35,570
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,270
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:49,630
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:54,280
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,380
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:03,400
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,970
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:10,110
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:14,710
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:20,060
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,860
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:26,480
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 31 =

20
00:01:39,420 --> 00:01:40,580
The court meeting is on tomorrow morning,

21
00:01:40,860 --> 00:01:42,740
so I can’t drink with you tonight.

22
00:01:43,020 --> 00:01:43,900
Liaozi

23
00:01:44,100 --> 00:01:45,620
can bring the liquor back to my chamber.

24
00:01:58,940 --> 00:01:59,900
Ms. Xiu and Ling’er,

25
00:02:00,340 --> 00:02:01,180
the first month

26
00:02:01,380 --> 00:02:03,220
is the busiest.

27
00:02:03,380 --> 00:02:04,380
The Empress is occupied.

28
00:02:04,420 --> 00:02:05,420
Don’t be slack

29
00:02:05,420 --> 00:02:06,620
and take good care of her.

30
00:02:07,260 --> 00:02:08,220
Starting from this year,

31
00:02:08,220 --> 00:02:11,100
your salaries for the first month will be doubled.

32
00:02:12,020 --> 00:02:13,900
I’ll have Ren Shouzhong

33
00:02:13,900 --> 00:02:15,460
bring you Korean ginseng tomorrow.

34
00:02:15,460 --> 00:02:17,820
Make ginseng soup for the Empress.

35
00:02:18,780 --> 00:02:19,620
Yes.

36
00:02:25,540 --> 00:02:26,260
Let’s go.

37
00:02:51,700 --> 00:02:52,500
Your Highness.

38
00:02:56,020 --> 00:02:56,780
Your Highness.

39
00:02:58,140 --> 00:02:59,860
I won’t go back tonight.

40
00:03:00,300 --> 00:03:01,380
I’ll stay with you.

41
00:03:33,380 --> 00:03:34,060
Liaozi,

42
00:03:35,380 --> 00:03:37,420
since when have you been with me?

43
00:03:38,660 --> 00:03:39,900
I started to work in Your Majesty’s chamber

44
00:03:40,660 --> 00:03:42,220
since 1032 A.D.

45
00:03:43,060 --> 00:03:43,820
But...

46
00:03:44,420 --> 00:03:47,580
But at first, you worked under Zhang Maoze.

47
00:03:53,060 --> 00:03:54,540
Only after the Empress Dowager’s death

48
00:03:55,580 --> 00:03:57,260
was I able to truly take charge.

49
00:03:58,940 --> 00:04:00,700
He’s my most trusted man

50
00:04:01,260 --> 00:04:02,420
with key posts

51
00:04:03,500 --> 00:04:05,580
in the Agency and the Imperial Office Bureau.

52
00:04:09,220 --> 00:04:13,180
You walked on eggshells around me

53
00:04:14,100 --> 00:04:15,940
and knew little about me,

54
00:04:17,700 --> 00:04:18,740
so you checked with him

55
00:04:19,620 --> 00:04:20,740
about everything.

56
00:04:25,420 --> 00:04:27,140
You aren’t too shrewd,

57
00:04:27,700 --> 00:04:28,820
but after all these years of service,

58
00:04:30,260 --> 00:04:31,100
you no longer need

59
00:04:32,340 --> 00:04:33,300
to consult him

60
00:04:33,300 --> 00:04:34,620
all the time.

61
00:04:41,260 --> 00:04:42,500
Sometimes, I wonder

62
00:04:43,380 --> 00:04:44,420
what you people

63
00:04:44,420 --> 00:04:45,900
think of me

64
00:04:46,700 --> 00:04:49,180
that you always have to be vigilant near me.

65
00:04:50,260 --> 00:04:52,700
If I break the law,

66
00:04:53,220 --> 00:04:55,180
you must uphold justice

67
00:04:55,580 --> 00:04:58,260
with words, actions or even force.

68
00:05:05,420 --> 00:05:06,180
Rise.

69
00:05:09,220 --> 00:05:10,820
You’re free to think of anything.

70
00:05:15,540 --> 00:05:17,580
Deep down inside, whether you’re good or bad,

71
00:05:18,300 --> 00:05:20,220
you like me or not,

72
00:05:20,900 --> 00:05:23,300
you’re loyal or disloyal,

73
00:05:24,700 --> 00:05:25,860
it’s all fine.

74
00:05:28,500 --> 00:05:29,380
You too.

75
00:05:30,900 --> 00:05:32,740
As long as you’re law-abiding,

76
00:05:33,500 --> 00:05:35,140
just be

77
00:05:35,860 --> 00:05:37,500
wherever you should be.

78
00:05:51,900 --> 00:05:52,580
Alright.

79
00:05:54,140 --> 00:05:54,860
Let’s go back.

80
00:06:14,580 --> 00:06:16,540
Taste this dessert made yesterday.

81
00:06:17,620 --> 00:06:18,900
Zongshi and Taotao

82
00:06:18,900 --> 00:06:20,460
grew up together.

83
00:06:20,980 --> 00:06:23,340
His Majesty said he’d officiate at their wedding.

84
00:06:25,500 --> 00:06:26,900
Are Zongshi and Taotao

85
00:06:26,900 --> 00:06:27,940
coming back?

86
00:06:29,460 --> 00:06:32,100
Huirou, where are your manners?

87
00:06:33,300 --> 00:06:34,740
Greetings, Madam Yu.

88
00:06:36,380 --> 00:06:38,020
Are Zongshi and Taotao

89
00:06:38,020 --> 00:06:38,980
coming back?

90
00:06:40,660 --> 00:06:41,540
= Concubine Yu =
Oh, silly.

91
00:06:41,660 --> 00:06:42,820
They won’t come back

92
00:06:42,820 --> 00:06:44,260
after moving out.

93
00:06:44,780 --> 00:06:46,020
Now that their marriage is settled

94
00:06:46,020 --> 00:06:47,420
and they’ve engaged,

95
00:06:47,660 --> 00:06:48,700
they can no longer

96
00:06:48,700 --> 00:06:49,860
be as close as before.

97
00:06:50,260 --> 00:06:52,780
But once the knot is tied,

98
00:06:52,980 --> 00:06:54,380
they can be together forever.

99
00:06:55,500 --> 00:06:56,740
Tie the knot?

100
00:06:59,100 --> 00:07:00,740
Meaning getting married.

101
00:07:01,700 --> 00:07:03,340
Like father and Her Highness?

102
00:07:03,660 --> 00:07:04,380
Yes.

103
00:07:05,660 --> 00:07:07,900
His Majesty’s nephew will marry
the Empress’s niece.

104
00:07:08,460 --> 00:07:10,940
A prince is marrying a noble lady.

105
00:07:11,300 --> 00:07:12,180
Taotao and Zongshi

106
00:07:12,180 --> 00:07:13,700
have always been close.

107
00:07:14,180 --> 00:07:15,700
They’ll make a perfect couple.

108
00:07:17,460 --> 00:07:19,420
Like father and Her Highness?

109
00:07:20,260 --> 00:07:21,900
Taotao won’t agree to that.

110
00:07:22,540 --> 00:07:23,700
Don’t be rude.

111
00:07:25,260 --> 00:07:27,140
Taotao demands that Zongshi

112
00:07:27,140 --> 00:07:28,180
can only like her.

113
00:07:28,740 --> 00:07:29,580
Back then,

114
00:07:29,580 --> 00:07:31,140
when Zongshi spent more time with me,

115
00:07:31,380 --> 00:07:32,900
Taotao would be upset.

116
00:07:33,700 --> 00:07:34,660
He once

117
00:07:34,860 --> 00:07:36,100
helped Miss Zhou

118
00:07:36,100 --> 00:07:37,220
copy the book.

119
00:07:37,900 --> 00:07:39,820
Then Taotao didn’t talk to him for days

120
00:07:40,140 --> 00:07:41,860
until he promised

121
00:07:41,860 --> 00:07:43,340
to only help her in the future.

122
00:07:47,260 --> 00:07:49,100
Since His Majesty has Zuixinglai to be his heir,

123
00:07:49,260 --> 00:07:51,140
Zongshi will no longer ascend the throne.

124
00:07:51,700 --> 00:07:52,820
Usually, there are more than one wife

125
00:07:52,820 --> 00:07:54,260
in others’ households,

126
00:07:55,060 --> 00:07:56,340
but they aren’t the palace.

127
00:07:57,340 --> 00:07:58,740
If Taotao

128
00:07:58,740 --> 00:08:00,100
can tame Zongshi,

129
00:08:00,340 --> 00:08:01,500
she can keep him all to herself.

130
00:08:01,700 --> 00:08:03,100
Watch your words.

131
00:08:04,180 --> 00:08:05,540
Zuixinglai is young

132
00:08:06,380 --> 00:08:07,860
while His Majesty is still in his prime.

133
00:08:08,100 --> 00:08:09,780
Other concubines

134
00:08:09,780 --> 00:08:11,660
will give birth to more sons.

135
00:08:12,860 --> 00:08:14,220
Madam Miao,

136
00:08:14,420 --> 00:08:15,940
you can relax.

137
00:08:16,980 --> 00:08:17,980
You know what,

138
00:08:18,180 --> 00:08:19,900
when Zuixinglai was born,

139
00:08:20,380 --> 00:08:22,260
we were all truly happy for you.

140
00:08:23,980 --> 00:08:24,700
We aren’t able

141
00:08:24,700 --> 00:08:25,980
to have His Majesty’s children,

142
00:08:26,940 --> 00:08:28,420
so we sincerely hope the heir’s mother

143
00:08:29,060 --> 00:08:30,020
is a kind person.

144
00:08:31,500 --> 00:08:32,500
As for you–know-who,

145
00:08:33,100 --> 00:08:34,700
people, who seem to fawn on her,

146
00:08:35,020 --> 00:08:36,740
are all relived

147
00:08:37,780 --> 00:08:39,020
knowing that she gave birth to a girl.

148
00:08:39,820 --> 00:08:40,580
Madam Yu...

149
00:08:41,420 --> 00:08:42,180
Huirou.

150
00:08:43,100 --> 00:08:44,460
Don’t tell others

151
00:08:44,860 --> 00:08:46,180
about our private conversation.

152
00:08:49,340 --> 00:08:50,380
What did you paint?

153
00:08:50,380 --> 00:08:51,220
Let me see.

154
00:08:52,860 --> 00:08:54,420
It’s not good enough.

155
00:08:54,620 --> 00:08:56,180
I’m going to redo it.

156
00:09:01,540 --> 00:09:02,540
That girl.

157
00:09:03,340 --> 00:09:06,540
= Liang Huaiji =

158
00:09:07,860 --> 00:09:11,500
Huaiji, I don’t feel like painting today.

159
00:09:14,540 --> 00:09:17,780
I see. Have a rest, Princess.

160
00:09:18,060 --> 00:09:19,060
I’ll take my leave.

161
00:09:19,420 --> 00:09:20,060
No.

162
00:09:21,180 --> 00:09:22,620
Let’s chat.

163
00:09:41,460 --> 00:09:42,300
I didn’t eat

164
00:09:42,820 --> 00:09:44,220
this osmanthus cake yesterday.

165
00:09:44,940 --> 00:09:46,580
Mother only gives me one in a few days.

166
00:09:46,780 --> 00:09:47,660
Let’s eat it together.

167
00:09:49,340 --> 00:09:50,980
You can have it all, Princess.

168
00:09:55,100 --> 00:09:56,860
Are we the best friends or not?

169
00:09:59,780 --> 00:10:03,020
Huaiji, don’t turn me down

170
00:10:03,300 --> 00:10:04,420
or be too polite to me.

171
00:10:05,220 --> 00:10:06,220
If you do,

172
00:10:06,300 --> 00:10:08,660
I’ll be really, really mad.

173
00:10:09,940 --> 00:10:12,500
Huaiji, I just realized

174
00:10:13,740 --> 00:10:16,140
when someone tells the other

175
00:10:16,740 --> 00:10:18,940
“You’re good. I respect you”,

176
00:10:19,380 --> 00:10:23,100
it actually means I don’t like you

177
00:10:23,660 --> 00:10:25,860
and don’t want to see you.

178
00:10:27,260 --> 00:10:28,220
What do you mean, Princess?

179
00:10:30,500 --> 00:10:33,660
Father said that to Her Highness that day.

180
00:10:33,980 --> 00:10:35,900
He said she was never wrong,

181
00:10:36,540 --> 00:10:38,860
and even without him,

182
00:10:39,100 --> 00:10:40,900
she could still be a good empress.

183
00:10:41,740 --> 00:10:43,260
He didn’t blame her at all

184
00:10:43,980 --> 00:10:45,700
but she was heartbroken.

185
00:10:46,700 --> 00:10:49,100
She didn’t cry or say anything,

186
00:10:49,740 --> 00:10:50,860
but I know

187
00:10:51,580 --> 00:10:53,860
she felt 1,000

188
00:10:53,940 --> 00:10:54,820
or 10,000 times worse.

189
00:10:55,780 --> 00:10:56,740
Caution, Princess.

190
00:10:57,060 --> 00:10:58,060
Stop telling me

191
00:10:58,060 --> 00:10:59,740
to be cautious or what not.

192
00:11:00,580 --> 00:11:01,740
I’ve kept this for so long

193
00:11:02,220 --> 00:11:03,820
that I didn’t even tell my mother.

194
00:11:04,140 --> 00:11:05,700
I only told you.

195
00:11:08,420 --> 00:11:09,340
Princess…

196
00:11:11,380 --> 00:11:14,660
Huaiji, you’re my best friend.

197
00:11:15,860 --> 00:11:16,700
I won’t

198
00:11:16,940 --> 00:11:18,540
tell anyone else in the palace.

199
00:11:21,460 --> 00:11:22,220
I know.

200
00:11:24,260 --> 00:11:26,900
But your analogy isn’t appropriate.

201
00:11:28,180 --> 00:11:30,540
His Majesty and the Empress aren’t...

202
00:11:31,740 --> 00:11:32,780
That’s disrespectful.

203
00:11:33,820 --> 00:11:35,420
Maybe I’m wrong.

204
00:11:37,540 --> 00:11:40,300
Huaiji, telling someone you’re good,

205
00:11:40,380 --> 00:11:41,620
you’re better than anyone

206
00:11:42,260 --> 00:11:44,180
isn’t necessarily love.

207
00:11:44,980 --> 00:11:45,980
I just realized

208
00:11:47,220 --> 00:11:49,380
Her Highness is unhappy.

209
00:11:50,620 --> 00:11:51,980
So is everyone else

210
00:11:52,420 --> 00:11:53,580
in the palace.

211
00:11:58,340 --> 00:11:59,100
Deputy Chief Han.

212
00:12:00,580 --> 00:12:02,540
Did you just arrive in the Capital?

213
00:12:03,260 --> 00:12:04,060
This morning, to be precise.

214
00:12:05,140 --> 00:12:06,060
Maoze, do you know

215
00:12:06,100 --> 00:12:07,460
what I’m summoned

216
00:12:07,460 --> 00:12:08,420
so urgently for?

217
00:12:08,660 --> 00:12:10,260
His Majesty always trusts you.

218
00:12:10,340 --> 00:12:11,620
I’m sure it’s important.

219
00:12:12,420 --> 00:12:13,260
All I know is

220
00:12:13,620 --> 00:12:14,620
yesterday, at this hour,

221
00:12:14,740 --> 00:12:15,820
His Majesty met with

222
00:12:16,060 --> 00:12:17,540
Fan Zhongyan at the Hall of Politics.

223
00:12:29,900 --> 00:12:34,140
I, Han Qi, pay respects to Your Majesty.

224
00:12:35,660 --> 00:12:36,740
The wind is strong in the northwest.

225
00:12:37,060 --> 00:12:39,700
Before you left the Capital two years ago,

226
00:12:39,700 --> 00:12:40,860
you weren’t this emaciated.

227
00:12:44,900 --> 00:12:46,860
I’m guilty about burdening Your Majesty

228
00:12:47,060 --> 00:12:48,220
with affairs at the border

229
00:12:48,860 --> 00:12:51,540
that Your Majesty even fell ill.

230
00:12:52,740 --> 00:12:54,220
I was told repeatedly

231
00:12:54,220 --> 00:12:55,380
not to be hasty,

232
00:12:55,860 --> 00:12:57,740
but I acted against it.

233
00:12:58,660 --> 00:12:59,740
The loss at Haoshuichuan...

234
00:13:03,420 --> 00:13:07,660
I...I’ll take full responsibility.

235
00:13:20,620 --> 00:13:24,220
It’s not entirely your fault.

236
00:13:25,740 --> 00:13:26,660
Those who served under you,

237
00:13:27,620 --> 00:13:29,340
such as General Ren Fu,

238
00:13:29,540 --> 00:13:30,820
were brave but reckless.

239
00:13:31,460 --> 00:13:32,300
I’m above you,

240
00:13:33,540 --> 00:13:36,260
and couldn’t suppress

241
00:13:36,340 --> 00:13:37,980
my desire to win.

242
00:13:39,740 --> 00:13:40,820
You were

243
00:13:41,900 --> 00:13:43,180
well aware of that,

244
00:13:45,020 --> 00:13:46,380
which led to this failure.

245
00:13:49,340 --> 00:13:51,100
Don’t be too harsh on yourself.

246
00:14:01,220 --> 00:14:02,060
Do you recognize this?

247
00:14:06,620 --> 00:14:07,900
It’s Minister Lv’s handwriting.

248
00:14:08,740 --> 00:14:13,140
But it doesn’t look

249
00:14:14,500 --> 00:14:15,780
as sharp as before.

250
00:14:18,460 --> 00:14:19,660
He’s been sick for long

251
00:14:20,140 --> 00:14:21,180
and his condition has worsened lately.

252
00:14:23,420 --> 00:14:25,700
He had Zhang Dexiang

253
00:14:26,060 --> 00:14:28,100
bring me this a few days ago.

254
00:14:30,220 --> 00:14:31,620
Feng Shiyuan’s case

255
00:14:32,460 --> 00:14:34,100
makes me realize the maladies we’re facing.

256
00:14:34,460 --> 00:14:37,420
The excess of officials slows down the court

257
00:14:38,220 --> 00:14:42,620
and leads to corruption, deception and oppression.

258
00:14:47,340 --> 00:14:49,540
It’s a poison to the state and the people.

259
00:14:50,140 --> 00:14:51,340
We must get rid of it.

260
00:14:52,580 --> 00:14:54,860
I discussed it with Lv Yijian more than once,

261
00:14:55,420 --> 00:14:56,780
but he kept saying

262
00:14:57,820 --> 00:14:59,940
that my concern is reasonable

263
00:15:01,220 --> 00:15:03,260
but most reformers in history

264
00:15:03,540 --> 00:15:04,660
ended up tragic.

265
00:15:05,900 --> 00:15:07,940
When I visited him last month,

266
00:15:08,540 --> 00:15:10,300
he brought up the reform himself

267
00:15:10,580 --> 00:15:11,500
and asked what I thought

268
00:15:12,220 --> 00:15:14,700
was the key to a successful reform.

269
00:15:15,980 --> 00:15:18,220
I said to win people’s trust.

270
00:15:24,940 --> 00:15:25,940
He said

271
00:15:26,940 --> 00:15:28,540
this was his last advice

272
00:15:29,340 --> 00:15:30,540
to me.

273
00:15:31,700 --> 00:15:32,780
He quoted the sages’ words

274
00:15:33,740 --> 00:15:36,300
to tell me how to win people’s trust.

275
00:15:39,540 --> 00:15:40,700
Appoint the righteous

276
00:15:41,340 --> 00:15:42,180
and abandon the corrupted,

277
00:15:42,860 --> 00:15:44,500
then people are willing to support them.

278
00:15:45,020 --> 00:15:47,300
Otherwise, discontent will grow.

279
00:15:48,740 --> 00:15:50,060
Minister Lv’s words...

280
00:15:50,420 --> 00:15:51,540
I can’t agree more to it.

281
00:15:52,260 --> 00:15:53,300
That’s why I’ve decided

282
00:15:53,740 --> 00:15:54,900
to appoint the ones regarded by the court

283
00:15:54,900 --> 00:15:56,140
and the masses

284
00:15:56,140 --> 00:15:57,300
as the most righteous,

285
00:15:59,140 --> 00:16:01,500
Fan Zhongyan, Han Qi and Fu Bi,

286
00:16:01,820 --> 00:16:04,020
to serve in the Cabinet
and Privy Council to lead the reform.

287
00:16:17,540 --> 00:16:18,460
Currently,

288
00:16:18,900 --> 00:16:20,660
official management

289
00:16:20,660 --> 00:16:22,500
should take precedence.

290
00:16:23,220 --> 00:16:24,060
Officials include

291
00:16:24,140 --> 00:16:26,300
present and future ones.

292
00:16:26,940 --> 00:16:28,220
= Fan Zhongyan, courtesy name Xiwen =
Clarify standards of promotion and demotion

293
00:16:28,500 --> 00:16:29,620
of current officials.

294
00:16:30,060 --> 00:16:33,340
Selecting future officials by the exam.

295
00:16:41,140 --> 00:16:42,380
I understand that perfume

296
00:16:42,380 --> 00:16:43,660
is your daily necessity.

297
00:16:44,620 --> 00:16:46,460
Due to the lockdown at the west border,

298
00:16:46,780 --> 00:16:48,180
spices from the west are too expensive.

299
00:16:48,820 --> 00:16:50,420
There are complaints among the masses.

300
00:16:51,500 --> 00:16:52,460
I know

301
00:16:52,500 --> 00:16:53,780
you can afford foreign spices,

302
00:16:54,420 --> 00:16:55,620
but sharing His Majesty’s burden

303
00:16:55,900 --> 00:16:57,660
and promoting thrift

304
00:16:57,860 --> 00:16:59,460
= Wang Gongchen’s wife Xue Yuhu =
is our responsibility.

305
00:16:59,900 --> 00:17:01,780
After consulting other concubines,

306
00:17:02,060 --> 00:17:03,820
I came up with an interesting competition

307
00:17:04,300 --> 00:17:06,260
to make and compare the perfume.

308
00:17:09,420 --> 00:17:11,500
= Elder Princess of Wei =

309
00:17:23,740 --> 00:17:25,300
Concubines have selected

310
00:17:25,620 --> 00:17:26,980
perfume makers

311
00:17:26,980 --> 00:17:28,340
from the Bureau of Clothing.

312
00:17:29,140 --> 00:17:30,500
They have their own recipes

313
00:17:30,900 --> 00:17:31,900
and the concubines fund them.

314
00:17:32,540 --> 00:17:34,220
Or they make the perfume

315
00:17:34,540 --> 00:17:35,940
according to concubines’ recipes.

316
00:17:36,900 --> 00:17:38,300
Among the solid perfume balls they made,

317
00:17:39,140 --> 00:17:40,420
please pick out

318
00:17:41,140 --> 00:17:43,620
the most unique,

319
00:17:44,020 --> 00:17:45,100
soothing

320
00:17:45,460 --> 00:17:47,700
and the cheapest one.

321
00:18:09,260 --> 00:18:10,500
Madam Zhang, I remember you said

322
00:18:10,500 --> 00:18:12,180
you hadn’t recovered after giving birth,

323
00:18:13,020 --> 00:18:15,460
so you wouldn’t attend any event this month.

324
00:18:16,540 --> 00:18:17,180
Today,

325
00:18:17,180 --> 00:18:19,220
you look radiant.

326
00:18:19,940 --> 00:18:21,020
Have you had lunch?

327
00:18:22,060 --> 00:18:23,380
Do you want to join us?

328
00:18:25,700 --> 00:18:27,460
My daughter still needs me all the time.

329
00:18:28,540 --> 00:18:30,740
I don’t trust others to take care of her.

330
00:18:31,420 --> 00:18:32,780
Right now, she’s asleep now

331
00:18:33,660 --> 00:18:34,700
so I came

332
00:18:35,540 --> 00:18:37,580
to join your perfume appreciation event.

333
00:18:43,020 --> 00:18:45,780
Prepare a seat and tea for Madam Zhang.

334
00:19:07,220 --> 00:19:09,820
I’m not here for appreciation only.

335
00:19:11,620 --> 00:19:12,820
At first,

336
00:19:13,500 --> 00:19:14,900
I only made perfume to keep myself busy,

337
00:19:16,220 --> 00:19:17,580
and I had no intention

338
00:19:17,820 --> 00:19:19,420
to take part in any competition.

339
00:19:21,140 --> 00:19:22,380
When His Majesty

340
00:19:22,820 --> 00:19:23,980
was with me earlier,

341
00:19:24,580 --> 00:19:25,580
he loved my perfume

342
00:19:26,900 --> 00:19:31,060
and said it was out of this world.

343
00:19:31,940 --> 00:19:35,220
He asked me to share it with others,

344
00:19:37,460 --> 00:19:38,260
so,

345
00:19:38,740 --> 00:19:40,940
I told Jingnu to make it according to my recipe

346
00:19:41,980 --> 00:19:43,100
and brought it here.

347
00:19:46,020 --> 00:19:47,380
That’s great.

348
00:19:54,940 --> 00:19:56,180
Just now,

349
00:19:57,020 --> 00:19:59,140
Chief Gu, Maid Xu and I

350
00:19:59,260 --> 00:20:00,660
watched the maids

351
00:20:00,740 --> 00:20:02,260
put the solid perfume balls

352
00:20:02,460 --> 00:20:04,380
= Xu Jingnu =
from eight concubines

353
00:20:04,620 --> 00:20:06,500
into the censers.

354
00:20:07,180 --> 00:20:08,940
As you can see,

355
00:20:09,420 --> 00:20:11,020
all the censers are marked with numbers.

356
00:20:12,060 --> 00:20:12,940
You won’t know

357
00:20:12,940 --> 00:20:14,380
whose perfume

358
00:20:14,380 --> 00:20:15,820
is in which censer.

359
00:20:16,180 --> 00:20:17,420
Only Chief Gu,

360
00:20:17,420 --> 00:20:18,900
Maid Xu and I know.

361
00:20:19,260 --> 00:20:19,980
= Gu Cai’er =
Later,

362
00:20:19,980 --> 00:20:21,420
we’ll place all eight censers

363
00:20:21,580 --> 00:20:23,460
in the back chamber

364
00:20:24,060 --> 00:20:25,940
for you to smell and judge.

365
00:20:26,660 --> 00:20:28,580
You can vote

366
00:20:28,580 --> 00:20:29,860
for the one you like the most.

367
00:20:30,780 --> 00:20:32,140
After voting,

368
00:20:32,580 --> 00:20:33,900
you can get its recipe

369
00:20:33,900 --> 00:20:36,340
and two perfume balls.

370
00:20:36,740 --> 00:20:37,860
The one with the highest votes

371
00:20:38,460 --> 00:20:40,620
will receive Her Highness’s awards.

372
00:21:04,940 --> 00:21:06,220
Your elaborate discussions

373
00:21:06,740 --> 00:21:08,380
on the current political situation

374
00:21:08,660 --> 00:21:10,580
greatly encouraged

375
00:21:11,340 --> 00:21:12,420
and inspired me.

376
00:21:13,660 --> 00:21:14,580
Such discussions

377
00:21:15,260 --> 00:21:17,860
should be made official routines,

378
00:21:18,380 --> 00:21:20,180
which will guide the administration.

379
00:21:21,180 --> 00:21:22,540
I strongly agree

380
00:21:22,660 --> 00:21:23,860
with one sentence Mr. Fan said.

381
00:21:24,740 --> 00:21:27,980
Any reign, if long, is definitely flawed.

382
00:21:28,580 --> 00:21:31,180
Flaws, if ignored, will lead to disasters.

383
00:21:31,900 --> 00:21:34,580
The traditional system is good

384
00:21:35,380 --> 00:21:38,020
but as time goes by,

385
00:21:38,860 --> 00:21:41,100
rules have become loose

386
00:21:41,340 --> 00:21:43,540
and rewards are granted extravagantly,

387
00:21:43,780 --> 00:21:45,180
causing the three excesses.

388
00:21:46,460 --> 00:21:47,300
The Book of Changes says,

389
00:21:47,740 --> 00:21:51,140
“Changes break limits
and induce flexibility and stability”.

390
00:21:51,740 --> 00:21:54,260
Therefore, to restore the law and order,

391
00:21:55,060 --> 00:21:56,980
changes must be made.

392
00:22:24,460 --> 00:22:25,740
Among the eight perfumes,

393
00:22:26,300 --> 00:22:27,340
Sweet Home

394
00:22:27,460 --> 00:22:29,900
made by Maid Xu

395
00:22:30,380 --> 00:22:32,540
and Tipsy Breeze

396
00:22:32,580 --> 00:22:33,300
I made

397
00:22:33,380 --> 00:22:34,420
are tied at the votes.

398
00:22:35,860 --> 00:22:38,020
But according to the rule,

399
00:22:39,580 --> 00:22:41,780
the cost of Maid Xu’s perfume

400
00:22:42,260 --> 00:22:43,820
is only one-tenth of mine,

401
00:22:44,660 --> 00:22:47,180
so she’s the winner.

402
00:22:56,820 --> 00:22:57,820
Please have a look.

403
00:23:05,580 --> 00:23:06,860
Congratulations, Madam Zhang.

404
00:23:08,740 --> 00:23:11,020
It’s just a game.

405
00:23:11,580 --> 00:23:12,460
The result doesn’t matter.

406
00:23:25,660 --> 00:23:27,980
Jingnu, look.

407
00:23:29,500 --> 00:23:31,100
These are the prizes

408
00:23:31,260 --> 00:23:32,460
I prepared for this competition.

409
00:24:23,780 --> 00:24:25,620
I accidentally stepped on my robe.

410
00:24:26,060 --> 00:24:27,300
Please forgive me.

411
00:24:30,660 --> 00:24:32,420
How embarrassing!

412
00:24:33,380 --> 00:24:34,140
You were carried away

413
00:24:34,140 --> 00:24:35,620
by a few prizes

414
00:24:36,860 --> 00:24:38,820
from Her Highness.

415
00:24:39,540 --> 00:24:41,140
Could you pay the price

416
00:24:41,860 --> 00:24:43,540
for breaking Her Highness’s gifts?

417
00:24:45,580 --> 00:24:48,620
Drag her out

418
00:24:48,780 --> 00:24:49,900
and club her 20 times.

419
00:24:50,860 --> 00:24:52,980
Please spare me!

420
00:24:53,140 --> 00:24:55,060
It’s...it’s my fault.

421
00:24:55,220 --> 00:24:56,340
I’m so sorry.

422
00:25:00,340 --> 00:25:02,100
They’ve been given to you,

423
00:25:02,460 --> 00:25:03,380
so they’re yours.

424
00:25:04,780 --> 00:25:06,460
You only broke your belongings.

425
00:25:07,340 --> 00:25:08,820
There are no such precedents

426
00:25:08,820 --> 00:25:10,180
that officials are punished

427
00:25:10,180 --> 00:25:11,060
for breaking gifts

428
00:25:11,540 --> 00:25:13,500
bestowed by His Majesty.

429
00:25:14,620 --> 00:25:17,220
Jingnu, you may leave.

430
00:25:22,740 --> 00:25:24,100
Have I pardoned you?

431
00:25:31,980 --> 00:25:34,740
Madam Zhang, Her Highness just said

432
00:25:35,460 --> 00:25:37,180
even if I broke

433
00:25:37,660 --> 00:25:39,060
gifts given to me,

434
00:25:39,740 --> 00:25:41,220
I wasn’t guilty.

435
00:25:43,660 --> 00:25:44,940
She’s pardoned you,

436
00:25:45,700 --> 00:25:46,740
but I didn’t.

437
00:25:48,100 --> 00:25:49,940
You’re less skilled than others

438
00:25:50,180 --> 00:25:51,140
at hairstyling and crown making.

439
00:25:51,500 --> 00:25:53,700
Finally, you won with my perfume,

440
00:25:54,180 --> 00:25:55,380
yet you got dizzy with success

441
00:25:56,260 --> 00:25:57,780
and embarrassed me.

442
00:25:59,980 --> 00:26:02,100
Get her out and beat her 20 times.

443
00:26:03,140 --> 00:26:05,620
Please spare me!

444
00:26:06,020 --> 00:26:07,380
I didn’t get dizzy.

445
00:26:07,540 --> 00:26:10,460
It’s...it’s all my fault. I’m sorry.

446
00:26:10,580 --> 00:26:11,620
Please forgive me.

447
00:26:11,620 --> 00:26:13,940
Your Highness, may I say something?

448
00:26:18,060 --> 00:26:18,860
Go ahead.

449
00:26:20,380 --> 00:26:21,660
According to my knowledge,

450
00:26:21,980 --> 00:26:23,460
Xu Jingnu works at the Styling Branch

451
00:26:23,460 --> 00:26:24,740
of the Bureau of Clothing.

452
00:26:24,980 --> 00:26:27,180
Although she’s asked to serve Madam Zhang,

453
00:26:27,740 --> 00:26:29,420
she isn’t her personal maid.

454
00:26:29,860 --> 00:26:31,060
Just like Qiuhe,

455
00:26:31,340 --> 00:26:32,660
although my mother likes her

456
00:26:32,740 --> 00:26:33,900
and asks her to do her hair,

457
00:26:34,260 --> 00:26:35,940
if other concubines ask for her service,

458
00:26:36,460 --> 00:26:37,740
my mother can’t stop her from going.

459
00:26:38,100 --> 00:26:39,380
Am I right?

460
00:26:41,340 --> 00:26:42,020
Yes,

461
00:26:42,460 --> 00:26:43,740
Neither did Xu Jingnu

462
00:26:43,740 --> 00:26:45,620
make mistakes in Madam Zhang’s chamber,

463
00:26:45,940 --> 00:26:48,220
nor did her break things there

464
00:26:48,580 --> 00:26:50,460
or hurt Madam Zhang,

465
00:26:50,980 --> 00:26:51,980
and Your Highness

466
00:26:51,980 --> 00:26:53,900
has already pardoned her.

467
00:26:54,540 --> 00:26:57,340
That makes Madam Zhang’s demand

468
00:26:57,340 --> 00:26:59,700
for punishing Xu Jingnu in public

469
00:27:00,260 --> 00:27:02,740
a violation of the rules.

470
00:27:03,540 --> 00:27:04,340
Huirou.

471
00:27:07,940 --> 00:27:08,980
You’re still a child.

472
00:27:09,780 --> 00:27:10,820
Even though your argument is correct,

473
00:27:11,060 --> 00:27:12,100
it’s disrespectful.

474
00:27:15,180 --> 00:27:16,340
Apologize to Madam Zhang.

475
00:27:24,660 --> 00:27:25,620
Madam Zhang.

476
00:27:26,380 --> 00:27:28,700
I wasn’t respectful enough.

477
00:27:29,380 --> 00:27:30,300
I apologize.

478
00:27:50,980 --> 00:27:52,500
I dare not accept

479
00:27:52,940 --> 00:27:53,940
Princess Fukang’s apology.

480
00:27:58,740 --> 00:28:00,060
My daughter should be awake

481
00:28:00,220 --> 00:28:01,340
and looking for me right now.

482
00:28:02,340 --> 00:28:03,980
I’ll take my leave.

483
00:28:17,980 --> 00:28:19,940
Jingnu, you may rise.

484
00:28:27,060 --> 00:28:28,140
There are perfume balls

485
00:28:28,140 --> 00:28:29,740
and recipes in the back chamber.

486
00:28:30,380 --> 00:28:31,020
Ladies,

487
00:28:31,460 --> 00:28:33,460
you can pick the ones you like.

488
00:28:43,940 --> 00:28:44,660
Clearly, Xu Jingnu

489
00:28:44,660 --> 00:28:46,260
was carrying out Madam Zhang’s order

490
00:28:46,380 --> 00:28:47,540
to humiliate Her Highness.

491
00:28:48,140 --> 00:28:49,900
Her Highness pardoned her

492
00:28:50,820 --> 00:28:52,260
but she tried to make a scene.

493
00:28:52,940 --> 00:28:54,820
I noticed that

494
00:28:55,460 --> 00:28:56,700
when she started to scold Xu Jingnu,

495
00:28:57,020 --> 00:28:58,100
her anger was fake.

496
00:28:58,700 --> 00:29:00,020
But it became real when Xu Jingnu said

497
00:29:00,380 --> 00:29:03,100
“Her Highness has already pardoned me”.

498
00:29:05,260 --> 00:29:06,780
That girl is dull.

499
00:29:07,620 --> 00:29:09,180
She assumed she’d be rewarded

500
00:29:09,180 --> 00:29:10,700
by Madam Zhang

501
00:29:10,740 --> 00:29:11,980
at the risk of

502
00:29:12,620 --> 00:29:13,900
being punished

503
00:29:14,580 --> 00:29:16,460
by Her Highness,

504
00:29:17,540 --> 00:29:19,420
yet what she said

505
00:29:19,780 --> 00:29:21,340
implied that

506
00:29:21,860 --> 00:29:23,100
others can’t disobey

507
00:29:23,420 --> 00:29:25,020
Her Highness’s words.

508
00:29:25,980 --> 00:29:27,740
Of course, she got infuriated.

509
00:29:28,980 --> 00:29:30,740
Who does she think she is?

510
00:29:31,820 --> 00:29:32,460
Everyone in this harem

511
00:29:32,460 --> 00:29:33,940
should follow Her Highness’s orders.

512
00:29:35,780 --> 00:29:37,060
She wants to top the Empress?

513
00:29:37,860 --> 00:29:39,380
This isn’t

514
00:29:39,860 --> 00:29:41,220
the first time.

515
00:29:41,220 --> 00:29:42,060
On what ground?

516
00:29:42,060 --> 00:29:43,540
Don’t you know?

517
00:29:48,260 --> 00:29:49,220
Qiuhe’s perfume

518
00:29:49,220 --> 00:29:50,900
made during the competition

519
00:29:51,380 --> 00:29:52,620
is beyond perfect.

520
00:29:53,260 --> 00:29:54,940
Even scholars

521
00:29:54,940 --> 00:29:56,020
like Mr. Su and Mr. Song

522
00:29:56,180 --> 00:29:58,460
couldn’t help writing poems about it.

523
00:30:00,020 --> 00:30:03,300
Madam Zhang’s perfume is unique,

524
00:30:04,140 --> 00:30:05,540
but in terms of the quality,

525
00:30:05,940 --> 00:30:07,100
it’s not half as good.

526
00:30:07,780 --> 00:30:09,140
It only tied with Qiuhe’s for two reasons.

527
00:30:10,260 --> 00:30:10,980
First,

528
00:30:11,940 --> 00:30:13,860
that woman is on the rise

529
00:30:15,140 --> 00:30:16,220
and has gained some support

530
00:30:16,500 --> 00:30:18,100
from other ladies.

531
00:30:19,460 --> 00:30:20,220
Second,

532
00:30:21,180 --> 00:30:23,260
she mentioned His Majesty.

533
00:30:27,140 --> 00:30:29,020
Who wouldn’t want

534
00:30:29,020 --> 00:30:30,580
to pander to His Majesty’s preferences?

535
00:30:31,540 --> 00:30:33,460
Other than that, among all the ladies present,

536
00:30:34,700 --> 00:30:36,340
however much they dislike her,

537
00:30:37,780 --> 00:30:39,660
they envy her

538
00:30:40,460 --> 00:30:41,780
being loved so much by His Majesty.

539
00:30:42,740 --> 00:30:44,260
Of course they want to copy her move,

540
00:30:44,580 --> 00:30:45,820
eat what she has

541
00:30:46,500 --> 00:30:47,860
and have what she owns.

542
00:30:50,940 --> 00:30:52,140
Exactly.

543
00:30:55,820 --> 00:30:57,460
I didn’t know

544
00:30:57,980 --> 00:30:58,660
you could also

545
00:30:58,660 --> 00:31:00,140
be so observant.

546
00:31:00,860 --> 00:31:02,300
His Majesty always says you’re slow

547
00:31:02,820 --> 00:31:04,820
because he has no knowledge of your wisdom.

548
00:31:07,540 --> 00:31:09,100
Stop teasing me.

549
00:31:10,340 --> 00:31:12,540
I used to only care about His Majesty

550
00:31:13,620 --> 00:31:15,380
without thinking about other things.

551
00:31:16,740 --> 00:31:20,500
When he came, I’d attend to his every need.

552
00:31:22,300 --> 00:31:23,260
If I couldn’t see him,

553
00:31:24,100 --> 00:31:25,980
I’d still think of him in my heart

554
00:31:26,660 --> 00:31:28,020
to help me carry on with my life.

555
00:31:31,060 --> 00:31:32,500
Now, I have Huirou

556
00:31:33,300 --> 00:31:34,660
and Zuixinglai.

557
00:31:37,060 --> 00:31:39,140
Naturally, I’m more cautious

558
00:31:39,540 --> 00:31:40,580
and sensitive for my children.

559
00:31:41,660 --> 00:31:43,940
You’ve seen Huirou’s personality.

560
00:31:48,780 --> 00:31:50,100
I’m worried

561
00:31:51,620 --> 00:31:52,860
even in my dream.

562
00:31:54,540 --> 00:31:56,300
If that narrow-minded woman

563
00:31:56,780 --> 00:31:58,740
becomes more powerful than Her Highness,

564
00:31:59,540 --> 00:32:01,620
she’ll harm my daughter.

565
00:32:05,940 --> 00:32:07,980
“Since 1004 A.D., during the late Emperor’s reign,

566
00:32:08,340 --> 00:32:10,100
civil and military officials get promoted

567
00:32:10,180 --> 00:32:11,820
every three and five years respectively

568
00:32:12,220 --> 00:32:14,380
without considering their achievements or ability.

569
00:32:15,260 --> 00:32:18,020
If there’s a wise man among the slow-witted

570
00:32:18,460 --> 00:32:20,780
dedicated to promoting good and punishing evil,

571
00:32:21,060 --> 00:32:22,780
the rest will accuse him of stirring up trouble

572
00:32:23,340 --> 00:32:27,180
and will be jealous of him and mock him.

573
00:32:27,500 --> 00:32:30,900
If he’s slightly wrong,
the rest will gang up against him”.

574
00:32:33,220 --> 00:32:34,100
Brilliant!

575
00:32:37,660 --> 00:32:38,500
Danshu,

576
00:32:40,740 --> 00:32:43,500
do you remember I once told you...

577
00:32:54,260 --> 00:32:55,060
Remember to

578
00:32:55,180 --> 00:32:56,540
bring Fan Zhongyan’s proposal

579
00:32:56,660 --> 00:32:57,620
to the Empress’s chamber later.

580
00:32:57,900 --> 00:33:00,940
She loves his works.

581
00:33:04,860 --> 00:33:05,940
I’m going out for a walk.

582
00:33:13,020 --> 00:33:13,860
No need to follow me.

583
00:33:14,100 --> 00:33:14,940
I just need some fresh air

584
00:33:15,740 --> 00:33:16,700
and I’ll be back after sunset.

585
00:33:32,900 --> 00:33:33,540
Princess.

586
00:33:34,780 --> 00:33:36,180
Is father having dinner?

587
00:33:36,580 --> 00:33:37,580
Are you off duty?

588
00:33:38,460 --> 00:33:39,220
His Majesty isn’t inside

589
00:33:39,660 --> 00:33:40,820
and is probably taking a walk.

590
00:33:41,900 --> 00:33:43,660
I was asked to bring something to Her Highness.

591
00:33:45,780 --> 00:33:47,420
I’ll go with you.

592
00:33:48,740 --> 00:33:49,460
Sure.

593
00:34:26,580 --> 00:34:27,420
Your Majesty.

594
00:34:35,180 --> 00:34:36,100
You are...

595
00:34:37,340 --> 00:34:40,020
Madam Miao’s combing maid?

596
00:34:41,180 --> 00:34:42,060
You’re...

597
00:34:42,660 --> 00:34:43,740
Dong Qiuhe, Your Majesty.

598
00:34:46,300 --> 00:34:47,140
Qiuhe.

599
00:34:48,380 --> 00:34:49,100
Rise.

600
00:34:56,460 --> 00:34:57,140
What’s wrong?

601
00:34:57,660 --> 00:34:58,660
Did someone upset you

602
00:34:58,660 --> 00:34:59,900
or are you in some sort of trouble?

603
00:35:06,060 --> 00:35:08,380
You’re smart and thoughtful.

604
00:35:08,900 --> 00:35:11,460
The Empress and Madam Miao both like you.

605
00:35:11,860 --> 00:35:12,940
What exactly happened

606
00:35:14,060 --> 00:35:15,220
that you couldn’t

607
00:35:15,540 --> 00:35:17,100
even ask the Empress for help?

608
00:35:18,500 --> 00:35:19,380
Did someone

609
00:35:20,260 --> 00:35:21,620
force you to do things

610
00:35:21,820 --> 00:35:23,060
against your will?

611
00:35:25,980 --> 00:35:28,380
I’m not in trouble

612
00:35:29,340 --> 00:35:30,660
but lost a competition

613
00:35:30,980 --> 00:35:32,980
that I was certain to win.

614
00:35:33,740 --> 00:35:35,220
I’m only mad at myself.

615
00:35:36,180 --> 00:35:37,140
It has nothing to do with others.

616
00:35:39,100 --> 00:35:40,220
That’s strange.

617
00:35:40,780 --> 00:35:42,300
During the previous hairstyling competition,

618
00:35:42,820 --> 00:35:44,060
the winner would be promoted.

619
00:35:44,220 --> 00:35:45,260
You lost

620
00:35:45,340 --> 00:35:47,380
but didn’t seem depressed at all.

621
00:35:48,460 --> 00:35:49,660
What was this competition about

622
00:35:50,580 --> 00:35:52,420
that made you cry quietly?

623
00:35:53,220 --> 00:35:54,620
Or did you also cry

624
00:35:55,300 --> 00:35:57,380
on the seventh night of July?

625
00:35:59,940 --> 00:36:00,940
That day,

626
00:36:01,380 --> 00:36:02,940
I didn’t think I lost.

627
00:36:05,740 --> 00:36:06,580
Your Majesty,

628
00:36:07,220 --> 00:36:10,100
was I really worse than others that day?

629
00:36:16,060 --> 00:36:16,940
Fine, fine, fine.

630
00:36:17,460 --> 00:36:19,580
I admit that you’re the best.

631
00:36:21,140 --> 00:36:22,780
I didn’t pick you

632
00:36:23,180 --> 00:36:24,380
for a reason.

633
00:36:25,180 --> 00:36:27,260
I’m more curious now.

634
00:36:28,220 --> 00:36:29,540
What competition did you lose

635
00:36:29,940 --> 00:36:31,220
this time?

636
00:36:35,540 --> 00:36:36,700
That’s about everything happened

637
00:36:36,700 --> 00:36:37,700
this afternoon.

638
00:36:38,100 --> 00:36:39,100
I don’t get it.

639
00:36:39,260 --> 00:36:41,300
Father is a gentleman.

640
00:36:41,340 --> 00:36:42,300
When his teeth

641
00:36:42,300 --> 00:36:43,780
were hurt by a little stone in his food,

642
00:36:43,780 --> 00:36:44,700
he didn’t allow me to say anything,

643
00:36:44,980 --> 00:36:46,740
or Officer Ren would punish the chefs.

644
00:36:46,860 --> 00:36:48,580
He said their negligence

645
00:36:48,580 --> 00:36:49,540
wasn’t a serious crime,

646
00:36:49,740 --> 00:36:51,100
but since his teeth were hurt,

647
00:36:51,300 --> 00:36:52,940
they’d be punished severely.

648
00:36:53,780 --> 00:36:55,580
How come a great man like father

649
00:36:55,780 --> 00:36:57,700
is attracted to such a mean and unruly woman

650
00:36:57,780 --> 00:36:58,980
but not Her Highness?

651
00:37:00,940 --> 00:37:01,780
What do you think?

652
00:37:02,220 --> 00:37:03,340
Don’t give me

653
00:37:03,340 --> 00:37:04,620
that you dare not say nonsense again.

654
00:37:04,740 --> 00:37:05,420
You know

655
00:37:05,420 --> 00:37:06,660
I won’t tell others.

656
00:37:08,580 --> 00:37:09,460
I’m thinking...

657
00:37:09,660 --> 00:37:10,420
What?

658
00:37:11,740 --> 00:37:13,260
If His Majesty didn’t like Her Highness,

659
00:37:13,860 --> 00:37:15,860
why would he be so eager

660
00:37:15,940 --> 00:37:17,260
to share good news at court with her?

661
00:37:18,140 --> 00:37:20,340
Even the most beloved women in history

662
00:37:20,540 --> 00:37:21,700
hardly had such a rare honor.

663
00:37:23,940 --> 00:37:25,140
But...

664
00:37:26,460 --> 00:37:27,580
But doesn’t father think

665
00:37:27,580 --> 00:37:28,980
Madam Zhang is wrong?

666
00:37:31,580 --> 00:37:32,580
If His Majesty

667
00:37:32,700 --> 00:37:34,220
indulged Madam Zhang’s every whim

668
00:37:34,660 --> 00:37:35,580
against the rules,

669
00:37:36,540 --> 00:37:38,660
why would he have asked her to change the outfit

670
00:37:38,820 --> 00:37:40,820
in the same color as the Empress’s in public?

671
00:37:41,660 --> 00:37:42,540
Why would he

672
00:37:42,620 --> 00:37:44,140
have forbidden her from using the Empress’s sedan?

673
00:37:45,420 --> 00:37:46,340
But...

674
00:37:46,820 --> 00:37:48,940
But father always gives her special treatment.

675
00:37:51,180 --> 00:37:54,220
His Majesty must care about her.

676
00:37:56,060 --> 00:37:58,820
You detest her rudeness,

677
00:37:59,660 --> 00:38:01,180
but His Majesty may not

678
00:38:01,620 --> 00:38:02,980
want to do anything about it.

679
00:38:03,980 --> 00:38:05,140
In her eyes,

680
00:38:05,140 --> 00:38:06,700
His Majesty must be different from others.

681
00:38:07,580 --> 00:38:08,740
She doesn’t like you

682
00:38:09,460 --> 00:38:10,900
but she sure loves His Majesty wholeheartedly.

683
00:38:13,980 --> 00:38:15,940
Huaiji, aren’t you coming in?

684
00:38:16,860 --> 00:38:18,980
Princess, it’s late.

685
00:38:19,860 --> 00:38:20,580
I still

686
00:38:20,580 --> 00:38:21,980
need to report back to His Majesty.

687
00:38:22,780 --> 00:38:24,020
I don’t like darkness.

688
00:38:24,260 --> 00:38:25,380
It scares me a little bit

689
00:38:25,740 --> 00:38:27,420
but not anymore

690
00:38:28,340 --> 00:38:29,980
because I have you

691
00:38:29,980 --> 00:38:31,060
with me at night.

692
00:38:46,940 --> 00:38:48,940
I’ve never tried your perfume

693
00:38:49,460 --> 00:38:50,780
but Madam Zhang’s

694
00:38:51,100 --> 00:38:53,220
is unique.

695
00:38:53,940 --> 00:38:54,900
Its scent

696
00:38:54,900 --> 00:38:56,540
is different from that of any spices.

697
00:38:57,220 --> 00:38:57,900
Yes,

698
00:38:58,420 --> 00:38:59,260
but...

699
00:38:59,580 --> 00:39:01,540
But in terms of the density

700
00:39:01,740 --> 00:39:02,900
and richness of the scent,

701
00:39:03,140 --> 00:39:04,100
it’s not of high quality.

702
00:39:05,980 --> 00:39:08,300
Quality aside,

703
00:39:08,500 --> 00:39:09,900
people’s preferences are as important.

704
00:39:10,740 --> 00:39:12,620
Since they ended up as a tie,

705
00:39:12,860 --> 00:39:13,900
they’re both good.

706
00:39:14,540 --> 00:39:16,180
I have no objection.

707
00:39:17,340 --> 00:39:18,260
However,

708
00:39:19,620 --> 00:39:21,580
the set of prize Xu Jingnu broke

709
00:39:21,580 --> 00:39:22,740
is valuable

710
00:39:22,820 --> 00:39:24,180
and a masterpiece.

711
00:39:24,740 --> 00:39:25,660
I was allowed to use it once

712
00:39:25,860 --> 00:39:27,580
when testing the perfume.

713
00:39:28,660 --> 00:39:30,740
When I heard that would be the prize,

714
00:39:30,900 --> 00:39:32,180
I couldn’t believe it.

715
00:39:32,860 --> 00:39:35,220
The Empress said she was strange to making perfume.

716
00:39:35,820 --> 00:39:36,940
Those tools

717
00:39:37,140 --> 00:39:38,420
would only sit there and collect dust

718
00:39:38,540 --> 00:39:40,580
in her hands.

719
00:39:42,140 --> 00:39:43,580
Despite what she said,

720
00:39:44,340 --> 00:39:46,140
I could sense her sincerity.

721
00:39:47,620 --> 00:39:50,500
Unfortunately, they ended up

722
00:39:51,340 --> 00:39:53,340
in the wrong hands because of my arrogance

723
00:39:53,780 --> 00:39:55,100
and got destroyed.

724
00:39:56,260 --> 00:39:57,900
It pained me deeply.

725
00:40:01,020 --> 00:40:02,260
You indeed love perfume.

726
00:40:03,780 --> 00:40:05,460
You cried over shattered tools

727
00:40:05,660 --> 00:40:07,940
just like generals mourned for horses’ deaths

728
00:40:08,500 --> 00:40:10,380
and broken swords saddened swordsmen.

729
00:40:11,700 --> 00:40:12,700
Don’t beat yourself up.

730
00:40:12,860 --> 00:40:13,580
Actually,

731
00:40:14,060 --> 00:40:16,020
