732
00:40:18,020 --> 00:40:19,980
You grew up with your grandfather

733
00:40:19,980 --> 00:40:21,180
who was an excellent perfume maker.

734
00:40:21,460 --> 00:40:22,420
Your skills

735
00:40:22,740 --> 00:40:24,340
and understanding of the perfume are exceptional.

736
00:40:25,220 --> 00:40:28,020
Those rules of perfume making

737
00:40:28,020 --> 00:40:29,100
are engraved on your mind.

738
00:40:29,420 --> 00:40:31,420
Even if you intended to be innovative,

739
00:40:31,860 --> 00:40:35,260
