740
00:40:36,220 --> 00:40:37,500
Madam Zhang is different.

741
00:40:38,340 --> 00:40:41,180
She has an agile mind

742
00:40:41,860 --> 00:40:43,260
but no experience,

743
00:40:44,420 --> 00:40:46,140
so it was her uniqueness

744
00:40:46,460 --> 00:40:48,420
that beat the perfume made by a master.

745
00:40:49,420 --> 00:40:50,340
That makes sense.

746
00:40:53,780 --> 00:40:54,500
Your Majesty,

747
00:40:54,740 --> 00:40:56,540
I’m far away from being a master.

748
00:40:56,860 --> 00:40:58,020
My family is simply...

749
00:40:58,220 --> 00:40:58,980
Calm down.

750
00:40:59,220 --> 00:41:00,220
Since you’ve come around,

751
00:41:00,220 --> 00:41:01,740
