763
00:41:28,140 --> 00:41:30,260
Since you lost the Empress’s prize,

764
00:41:31,820 --> 00:41:32,940
I can give you another one.

765
00:41:34,340 --> 00:41:35,340
I don’t deserve it.

766
00:41:37,100 --> 00:41:38,020
If you

767
00:41:38,340 --> 00:41:40,460
