768
00:41:41,860 --> 00:41:42,820
I dare not.

769
00:41:45,260 --> 00:41:47,020
You can’t think of anything at the moment

770
00:41:47,620 --> 00:41:49,260
and I can’t give you the same set of tools

771
00:41:49,260 --> 00:41:50,380
