772
00:41:52,620 --> 00:41:53,300
How about this?

773
00:41:54,260 --> 00:41:55,620
I’ll give you a promise instead.

774
00:41:56,060 --> 00:41:57,100
You can use it

775
00:41:57,580 --> 00:41:58,540
