784
00:42:15,140 --> 00:42:16,020
Thank you, Your Majesty.

785
00:42:17,900 --> 00:42:19,660
Alright, it’s late.

786
00:42:19,660 --> 00:42:20,500
I should go back.

787
00:42:21,340 --> 00:42:22,540
Chatting with you

788
00:42:23,020 --> 00:42:24,220
